2026-04-20T14:06:00.000+00:00 ‚úÖ `idx_orders_user_id` created ‚Äî non-blocking, took ~3 min.

### Step 2 ‚Äî Create index on `order_date` (range queries, reporting)
2026-04-20T14:06:00.001+00:00 ‚úÖ `idx_orders_order_date` created ‚Äî non-blocking.

